io.spine.validate

Class MessageValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.validate.MessageValue

  • @Immutable
public final class MessageValue
extends java.lang.Object
    A value of a Message to validate.
    Implementation Note:
    For the performance reasons the values of the passed Message fields are read either via reflection or directly if an instance of FieldAwareMessage is passed. Also, for the same reason the contents of non-oneof fields are cached once read.
